{"tid":908452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女工友躲太陽！坐「壓路機前」休息　下一秒遭輾斃","createTime":"2018-11-19T14:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T20:43:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":16,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"b85dc8426b774eb679f05c8572b3a79a58ec1a98","tid":908452,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨日前發生一起恐怖的工安意外，一名女性馬路維修工在休息時為了躲太陽，坐在壓路機前面休息，不料壓路機駕駛疑似沒有將壓路機固定好，意外讓壓路機隨斜坡滑下，直接將女子輾斃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/19/1649689-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2F1649689-XXL.jpg&h=54af16a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲女工友躲太陽坐「壓路機前」休息」，下一秒遭輾斃。（圖／翻攝自loykob）</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，事件發生於本月14日，柬埔寨國道5號線建設現場，一名38歲女作業員在休息時，疑似躲太陽坐在壓路機前面，不料駕駛沒將裝置固定好，導致因斜坡往下移動，直接將這名女作業員輾斃。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，發生意外的公司是一間小承包商，目前柬埔寨相關單位，已依「缺乏工安意識」、「未達施工安全標準」等，禁止該承包所有工程。（編輯：陳昱哲）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=458922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D458922&d=ayxGCzeFtYLQTdJ4vPfzYzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=da073e6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D458922&h=7aa8fbc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=458922</a>"},{"pid":"e30fc4de2a2c9874393b7076e95387e9a706ded4","tid":908452,"uid":101699,"like":148,"dislike":4,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"JoJo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09ca69182bf4e3a718332eac38c40fc98453d34","tid":908452,"uid":25858,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2da5d60f2c794c6eff70fa9a4bc70666e6bef5","tid":908452,"uid":41524,"like":117,"dislik